overview: When it comes to girls, two is always better than one. And thats exactly what our lucky guys will find out in Private Specials, Two Girls, Double the Fun where we stack the numbers and give them twice the workout! Everything multiplies in a threesome, twice the beauty, twice the fun, twice the asses, twice the bust, and thats especially of true of our girls Holly Molly, Rita Fox, Luna Umberley, Vivian Grace, Angie, Milana Minka, Emily and Mary Frost, who have all come to share a stallion with a friend and show you how we do things Private style!
title: Two Girls, Double the Fun
